OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thames Water's new chair has said      
OL,6, nationalisation is not the right way   
OL,7, forward despite the regulator warning  
OL,8, the company has "deep-rooted" problems.
OL,10,FSir Adrian Montague said he understood 
OL,11,Fcustomer "frustration" over the UK's   
OL,12,Flargest water firm's poor performance. 
OL,14,FBut he said the best way to resolve it 
OL,15,Fwas keeping the company under private  
OL,16,Fownership.                             
OL,18,FThames Water has faced criticism over  
OL,19,Fsewage discharges and leaks and is     
OL,20,Fstruggling under #14bn debts.          
